<br>
you can queue up things for the pet to attack by choosing one then another and so on.  Nice for fights with lots of unmezzable adds or where you have two tanks going at once in a raid.  Send the pet  on one and then target the other and give the attack  command then med.  Pet moves from the dead one to the other without any further interaction.. and usually the second tank has enough aggro that you sitting wont bother the MOB much when you pet starts beating it.  <br>
