<br>
Lvl 16-19, I think, the mage is fantastically overpowered.  Besides the increase in Pet power, the direct damage increase the mage gets at 16 is immense.  I had about zero problem beating the red cons at the Lake Rathe Aviak guards. (And it is not like this is the only place you could go to)   I would speculate that a typical mage would spend less time going from 16 to 20, than he will 12 to 16, since the mage completely dominates lvl 16.  (That I have seen, personally)  So, my further speculation is that if you are having trouble at lvl 17, it is not going to get any better.  <br>
<br>
